HOWTO: Compile Telepathy/Tapioca qt

1 - Get Gabble connection Manager

http://telepathy.freedesktop.org/releases/telepathy-gabble/telepathy-gabble-0.3.6.tar.gz

Use glib and LoudMouth
apt-get install libloudmouth1-dev

2 - Get Tapioca-qt and Telepathy-qt

svn co https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/tapioca-voip/trunk/telepathy-qt
svn co https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/tapioca-voip/trunk/tapioca-qt

Both use CMake so it's the same way to compile a KDE module.
